title: Gears of War Patch & Crack for Date Problem Fix
description:
NO NEED TO CHANGE DATE AGAIN AND AGAIN FOR PLAYING GEARS OF WAR.


1. First install Gears of War

2. Then Run GearsPC_Tu3_Microsoft

3. Copy Startup.exe to   C:\Program Files\Microsoft Games\Gears of War\Binaries\

4. Launch the game from desktop

5. Done


NOTE : If you already replaced the startup.exe in C:\Program Files\Microsoft Games\Gears of War\Binaries\ with other startup.exe that is not working, then copy and replace the original startup.exe from DVD to  C:\Program Files\Microsoft Games\Gears Of War\Binaries\  before installing the update.
